snippet.title: Symphonia | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Philemon is ready to bring the music back to the world of Symphonia. Are you? Symphonia is now out on PC, PlayStation, and Xbox. The Nintendo Switch version will launch in early 2025!

Awaken a musical realm in this poetic platformer. In Symphonia, you'll use the power of your violin coupled with your platforming skills to gather an orchestra to bring the musical machinery of the world back to life!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1865960/Symphonia/
Epic Game Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/symphonia-6d9781
GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/symphonia
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10008825
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/symphonia/9nblhdb0wlhz
